weather data assimilation framework. The effort will increase the model top from 30km to 70km and increase the
vertical fidelity of the model in the stratosphere in support of DoW capabilities operating/transiting through the
middle atmosphere. Additionally, a portion of the funding will be used to continue efforts with Windborne on High
Altitude Balloons [HABs] to capture data in the stratosphere and integrate the data into the MPAS and JEDI.
