FY 2025 to FY 2026 Increase/Decrease Statement:
FY 2025 to FY 2026 increase establishes a dedicated MFP team tasked to develop annual MFP software builds.
The MFP software will meet the new requirements of new mining systems, Quickstrike-ER, MK 68 CDM, and
the Encapsulated Effector which are under development and progressing towards fielding. The current MFP
software does not support these advanced mining systems.
