       Change Summary Explanation
       The FY 2026 request was reduced by $5.278 million for Advisory and Assistance Services to promote efficiencies and advance the policies of the Administration
       in alignment with Executive Order 14222, "Implementing the President's Department of Government Efficiency Cost Efficiency Initiative."

       The FY 2026 request was reduced by $6.616 million for civilian personnel to optimize the workforce in compliance with Executive Order 14210, "Implementing the
       President's Department of Government Efficiency Workforce Optimization Initiative."

       FY2026 funding was increased by $88.286:

       PU 3278: FY2026 funding request was increased by $42.226 to fund MQ-25 RDTEN obsolescence and critical software integration efforts not previously funded
       in FY26 after program restructure implemented in FY23 ($55.720) and reduced for rate/miscellaneous adjustments (-$13.494).

       FY2025 funding request was increased by $40.112 to fund MQ-25 RDTEN Congressional Action ($51.344) and reduced for miscellaneous adjustments (-
       $11.232).

       PU 3279: FY2026 funding request was increased by $46.060 to fund UMCS RDTEN critical software integration efforts not previously funded in FY26 to support
       MQ-25 program restructure implemented in FY23 ($48.000) and reduced for rate/miscellaneous adjustments (-$1.940).

       Schedule:
       PU 3278: R-4 Schedule Acquisition Milestone Knowledge points and Test Milestones were updated based on test air vehicle delivery delays from the Original
       Equipment Manufacturer (OEM).

       MQ-25 Air Vehicle (AV) deliveries have shifted due to delays in the build of Engineering Development Manufacturing (EDMs) and Static Demonstration Test
       Article (SDTAs) due to realized risk on first time system install (predominantly Fuel Tube quality escapes).

       PU 3279: R-4 Schedule updated to reflect current Aircraft Carrier, Nuclear (CVN) install schedule along with latest Unmanned Carrier Aviation (UCA) and CVN
       Test Windows.




