E. Acquisition Strategy
Using Software Acquisition Pathway (SWP), the acquisition strategy builds on agile software engineering methodologies and modernization of existing capabilities
utilizing evolutionary acquisition. Timelines are reduced by modularizing both software engineering solutions and the associated contracting and funding strategies. This
enables dynamic resource allocation based on current warfighter needs. The desired end state is continuous delivery of software. This program is dependent on support
from the All Domain Common Platform (ADCP).

