Title: Flight Test                                                                                                         0.000       4.725       5.406      0.000       5.406
Description: Contractor Flight Test support to continue contractor testing of new capabilities as required. Costs
include but not limited to maintenance on test aircraft, contractor engineering support for test related technical
and safety of flight issues, test planning, test analysis, and support of test execution. It also includes Edwards
AFB Flight Test Support where direct costs are related to flight testing and include ramp space, fuel, air traffic
control, range costs, etc., which are items each weapon system must pay when using Air Force flight test
locations.

